dragon (lightweight drag-and-drop source and target)
                                                                   
dragon provides a small GTK+3 window for dragging files into apps
that expect file-manager style drag-and-drop. It can also act as a
drop target and print received files or text to standard output.
                                                                   
It is useful from scripts and shells on X or Wayland systems.
                                                                   
Homepage: https://github.com/mwh/dragon
